title: EP.39: TOP FANTASY FOOTBALL SLEEPERS, NBA FINALS, NFL AWARD PREDICTIONS, 1V1 UPDATES, AND MUCH MORE!
description: Joe and Griffin go over who they think you should pick up in this years fantasy draft with the best sleeper picks of 2023. They also discuss the NBA finals and how things might shake out. With predictions for the NFL awards and one on one updates in this episode also. Tune in and find out more!
